quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,82,"No e Seytanuuji Й—in, Й—in Й—i no mutana mo, Й—i ngolla golle ga Й—um. Min laatanike Й—i ReenooЙ“e."
  21,83,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Ayyuuba tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, [O maaki:] "Min dey memii kam lorra kan, ko aan woni Й“uroowo Yurmeede yurmtooЙ“e Й“en"."
  21,84,"Min njaabinani mo Min kuГұci ko heЙ“i mo kon immorde e lorra, Min ngkkiti mo Й“eynguure makko nden e yeru maЙ“Й“e wond'ude e maЙ“Й“e kadi, Й—um ko Yurmeende immorde ka amen e waaju wona nde rewooЙ“e Й“en."
  21,85,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli, Й“en fow ko e muГұЙ“e Й“en Й“e njeyaa."
  21,86,"Min naadi Й“e e ndeer Yurmeende Amen nden, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“een."
  21,87,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Jannuuni tuma nde o yahnoo ko o tikkuЙ—o o sikki won'de Min njarribtaaka e hoore makko, o noddi ka niЙ“e; "Won'de deweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa An Senaare wonanii Ma, min dey mi laatike jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"."
  21,88,"Min njaabinani mo, Min ndaЙ—ndi mo immorde e suno ngo, ko wano nii kadi Min danndirta gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  21,89,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] fii Jakariyaa tuma nde o noddunoo Joomo makko, [o maaki:] Jooma, wota A Й—alam bajjo, ko aan woni ЖҒurЙ—o MoЖҙЖҙude ronooЙ“e Й“en."
  21,90,"Min njaabinani mo, Min ngokki mo Yahyaa, Min moЖҙЖҙinani mo sonnaajo makko on, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e yaccoo e [gollugol] moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hiЙ“e nodda Min ka reerЙ—eende e kulol Й“e laatinoke yannkinaniiЙ“e Min."